TestScheduler advances virtual time deterministically inside scheduler.run(...). Each frame in a marble string equals 1 virtual ms. Async operators that accept a SchedulerLike are auto-swapped for the TestScheduler, so delay(50) completes instantly in real time but correctly 50 virtual frames later on the diagram.

